{"tid":767312,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我到底做左啲咩錯事令你一個電話都唔聽，當我鬼咁避?","createTime":"2018-08-04T11:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T06:53:57.000Z","uid":50076,"like":2,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f9187c6c65f586fa7c3d9729853bf9ad73c8f2ba","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n我係做盡錯事，我係控制唔到脾氣。<br />\n<br />\n但你都唔洗一個電話都唔聽，搞到我成個癲佬咁打鑼打鼓咁搵你。<br />\n<br />\n玩消失好咩?<br />\n你肯聽我一個電話就得啦，我根本唔洗做咁多無聊野/騷擾你既野。<br />\n又搵你朋友，又用唔同apps 搵你，行街睇下撞唔撞到你。<br />\n<br />\n而家打一次比你，你就熄個幾鐘機。<br />\n每次都係一份痛苦黎架。<br />\n<br />\n我知係我錯啦，我唔求D咩啦，唔一齊就唔一齊，唔好消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458524a99cb7e7751cb3187831f166a6c143fcc6","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:27:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲可以話比我聽<br />\n係咩情況下先會一個電話都唔聽?<br />\n<br />\n我身心都好累。"},{"pid":"8462ba594e778ca3c6c7920c7c33a9e0200ee648","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:28:27.000Z","msg":"我好無助。<br />\n<br />\n兩個幾星期都訓得好差."},{"pid":"055400eaa51c3c795d7580e54fed12be512d1549","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲可以長期同我傾?<br />\n<br />\n帶我番出黎?"},{"pid":"8a3a7c60a18362e0a6b941a85ca7f60364dd07af","tid":767312,"uid":197954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"巴打放過別人等於放過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc30c189af32473634c4e7b2b9e681b8da54a3d4","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"搵佢，佢直程消失左。<br />\n<br />\n搵朋友，我驚搞到佢地反感。<br />\n<br />\n到底世上仲有冇人可以接納我同我傾?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己屈住好辛苦"},{"pid":"15a8d444f