怒一上腦，我就控制唔到。"},{"pid":"74974ad3e0437956c652638da0812a037e4c63eb","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f0f6cfa0b524e74aee00714e7d59a704012a8dce","tid":767312,"uid":48426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似情殺案情節"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:02:55.000Z","msg":"唔會啦，我點都唔會做得出犯法既事。"},{"pid":"fb87b1ef60028572e29dd2f9f74286e081a1fda1","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:05:26.000Z","msg":"快啲屌醒我<br />\n<br />\n屌之餘建議埋一啲方法比我控制脾氣。"},{"pid":"3b12728e40cba652f0dbd6079a698c4d36126cf1","tid":767312,"uid":63452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:07:30.000Z","msg":"係你錯在先重好怪人同合理化自己，講到人逼到你痴線咁，根本係你本身痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收手放過人啦</span></div></ins></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"019385149e2486c111bd602d1f5760115ce9af98","tid":767312,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b12728e40cba652f0dbd6079a698c4d36126cf1","tid":767312,"uid":63452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:07:30.000Z","msg":"係你錯在先重好怪人同合理化自己，講到人逼到你痴線咁，根本係你本身痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收手放過人啦</span></div></ins></em></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"我承認既...<br />\n<br />\n放過佢即係唔好再搵佢?"},{"pid":"4583aa17304cee6